import React from 'react'
import { List, ListItem, ListItemText} from '@material-ui/core/';

const Item = () => {
    return (
        <List>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemText
            primary="Times nacionais"
            secondary="3"
          />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemText
            primary="Times internacionais"
            secondary="3"
          />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemText
            primary="Times históricos"
            secondary="3"
          />
        </ListItem>
      </List>
    )
}

export default Item;
